\& #
\& # returns: value corresponding to openssl\*(Aqs X509_EXTENSION structure (0 on failure)
.Ve
.IP "\(bu" 4
X509_CRL_get_ext_by_NID
.Sp
\&\fB\s-1COMPATIBILITY:\s0\fR not available in Net\-SSLeay\-1.54 and before
