.Sp
Note: you can use \*(L"P_ASN1_STRING_get\*(R" to convert \s-1ASN1_OCTET_STRING\s0 into perl scalar variable.
.IP "\(bu" 4
X509_EXTENSION_get_object
.Sp
\&\fB\s-1COMPATIBILITY:\s0\fR not available in Net\-SSLeay\-1.45 and before
